        <abstract> 
<p>Michele Lessona will translate <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> into Italian [1871].</p>  
<p>Sends his review from <hi rend="italic">Nuova Antologia</hi> [17 (1871): 177–94].</p>  
<p>In a letter to <hi rend="italic">Archivio per l’Anthropologia</hi> he raises some doubts about sexual selection and proposes "Neogenesis" as a complement to natural selection in cases of rapid change.</p> 
        </abstract>
